MSCS specialises and has in excess of 40 years, recognised industry experience and specialises in the provision of civil engineering, earthmoving, mining and contracting services, in the following disciplines:

Civil Engineering, Earthmoving and Civil Construction Services
Mining Contracting Services and Heavy Mining Equipment Rental
Environmental Rehabilitation Toxic, Chemical, Industrial and Post Mining
Production of Hard Rock Quarry Raw Materials
Bulk Materials Transport and Heavy Vehicle Logistical Services
Mine Site Construction Services conducts business as follows:

We are committed to providing a healthy and safe working environment;
Engagement with the local communities in which we operate;
Creating employment for a wide range of people and sustaining their livelihoods;
Preserving environmental sustainability and bio-diversity;
Our commitment is to Corporate Social Responsibility and Principles of Responsible Investment in providing a sustainable environmental culture for our employees, clients and communities.

